page.title: 11South Park
page.content: South Park is the area of forest and heathland in the block.(North Park is used by the Ministry of Defence). South Park is a very peaceful place where many people go to walk their dogs and enjoy the peace and quiet. The only disturbance is the distant sound of the cars on the busy spur road to Bournemouth.The only other noises are the singing of the birds and the humming of grass hoppers. In the heather and gorse,there is the occasional spider's webb shining in the sun. In the wooded area,there is a woodland walk which is marked with white arrows.
